mobiJOBS I have invented over a period of 5 years that turns "any" mobile phone into a tool for accessing, my country of 50 million people has about  14million people unemployed, most people rely on  newspapers to access job listings but often 10 or less jobs would be shown, job advertisers like to advertise on the internet these days, but then again only 10% of people in my country have access to computers with internet, while on the other-hand 83% of people have cell phones, so it seems logical that the mobile phone should be the means through which job vacancy information is disseminated to people, thus the mobiJOBS culminated.

Job Seekers become members and pay a daily fee of about $0.29 US cents off their mobile phone accounts, currently we have 3000 subscribers that generate about $3571.42 US Dollars gross sales per month, the 3000 subscribers were gotten after a 2 minute interview on the largest radio station in my country with 3.6million listeners per week, therefore it seems logical to confidently predict  that if I could get an AD Campaign going for one month, that would certainly bring thousands of subscribers which would generate enough revenue to be able to invest back into more advertising campaigns, at present, though am generating revenue I would have to save for months to be able to afford to advertise on this particular radio station that yielded wonderful results previously. 

Loan Requirements:
Purpose: Advertise on national radio for one month.
Amount: $14285.71
Payback Period: 2months

**Amounts are in US dollars at an exchange rate of South African R7 against 1 US Dollar.

Please take a look at mobiJOBS website for more information on how the service works http://www.mobijobs.co.za
